name: Rapid Wire | Low-fi Wireframe kit
description:
Simple way to experience of sketching on a notepad, but using a Figma - one of the fastest software for designing UI.


Features:

  1. Auto Layout (with latest update)
  2. Variants
  3. Universal Components for Desktop and Other Apps
  4. Web Components
  5. iOS Components
  6. Android Components
  7. Wireflow (combination of wireframes and flowcharts)
  8. Custom Icons
  9. Landing Pages with 9 different design
  10. Visual design language
